About this item

  • Vivid Iris metal agave: you will get multiple sets of metal agave garden decorations. With 13 butterflies, they look realistic from a distance during the day and are a great addition to your garden decor. At night, solar it can light up your garden and make your patio porch more beautiful and dynamic.
  • 4 kinds of changing color Christmas lights: Solar butterflies will slowly change 4 different colors at night, they are like magical flower fairies, light up your garden, path, give you a wonderful experience. During the day, these realistic decorative lanterns are still very beautiful.
  • In bad weather: These IP67 waterproof solar outdoor lights are durable enough to stay outdoors, and they will operate and stay lit in any weather. So solar iris flowers can also be used in outdoor graves or cemeteries as memorial decorations.
  • Adjustable stem and leaves: Both stem and leaves are supported by wire for superior flexibility and durability. These flower bed decorations will bring you outdoor decorating solutions with solar garden lights. Suitable for planting near trees, flower beds, fences, cemeteries, graves and walkways.
  • solar Power: No wiring required, simply place the solar metal agave iris flower in the sun, turn on the switch and it will automatically work during the day and night, this beautiful and energy efficient yard light is the perfect gift for family and friends such as Mother's Day, Valentine's Day, Father's Day and more.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
